{
  "stem": "22463.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When she-- when we came to the court, the judge asked her whether that-- she is not [INAUDIBLE], or something of the kind, because he has some reservation because the trustee was in, was [INAUDIBLE] give her a [? go. ?] She-- by-- by chance, she find a partner of her sister-in-law in the court, and he was representing her.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a clerk-- clerk in-- in [INAUDIBLE] '37.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later I went to the-- to-- to make-- my-- my duty as a-- in the military-- Polish military.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I come back, I get proposition to be presented from this other place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Krakow district, that's all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So to-- I was, rather, very free-- wherever I want to go, I just have to come afternoon, give the report to the-- or whether I have some orders, or inquiries, and so on.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Six-- 18 months.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was have a very-- and there was a-- a chap who was-- going with my cousin for years.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was-- I believe he was a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the army who was fighting with the Australian-- Austrian people, against Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he has a connection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I believe that he was doing that for money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he told me-- usually, the-- the duty was 24 months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when I-- and I have to go wherever they send me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I ask whether they could arrange for me to-- to be in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he told me, yes, and there is a one thing to have this-- then you'll be much better off, because you'll be only 18 months, or something of this kind.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What job did you do, in the 18 months?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
